325
00:22:49.749 --> 00:22:50.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles!</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:22:50.748 --> 00:22:51.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:22:54.547 --> 00:22:55.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be quiet!</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:22:59.705 --> 00:23:01.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: That's one Black Hole</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>straight up, right?</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:23:03.664 --> 00:23:04.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Synthale, please.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:23:05.703 --> 00:23:06.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be right with you, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:23:17.860 --> 00:23:19.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quark, what about that synthale?</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:23:19.460 --> 00:23:20.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just another minute.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:23:25.297 --> 00:23:26.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quark?</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:23:26.577 --> 00:23:29.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, Chief, I'm a little busy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>right now.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:23:31.656 --> 00:23:33.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm in no mood for games, Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:23:33.695 --> 00:23:35.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So why don't you give me my drink</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:23:35.775 --> 00:23:38.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>or I break every bone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in your worthless little body.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:23:38.814 --> 00:23:41.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, just because your life's</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in shambles right now--</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:23:41.533 --> 00:23:42.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:23:43.933 --> 00:23:46.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One synthale coming right up.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:23:46.851 --> 00:23:47.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:24:14.203 --> 00:24:15.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles?</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:24:16.842 --> 00:24:17.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:24:18.802 --> 00:24:22.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What are you doing here?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I've never really been gone, have I?</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:24:24.440 --> 00:24:25.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not real.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:24:26.280 --> 00:24:27.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're just in my head.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:24:27.919 --> 00:24:29.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's all I ever was.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:24:30.679 --> 00:24:33.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I'm real to you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and that's all that matters.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:24:34.197 --> 00:24:35.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go away.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:24:35.757 --> 00:24:39.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm your friend. You need me.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:24:40.155 --> 00:24:42.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are the last thing I need.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:24:42.315 --> 00:24:45.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're wrong, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You need me, now more than ever.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:25:13.586 --> 00:25:14.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:25:15.505 --> 00:25:16.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to work.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:25:17.344 --> 00:25:22.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, as your friend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have to tell you I'm worried about you.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:25:27.261 --> 00:25:29.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't be. I'm home.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:25:30.212 --> 00:25:30.820 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm working</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:25:31.460 --> 00:25:33.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and for the first time in as long</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as I can remember</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:25:33.979 --> 00:25:34.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel good.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:25:36.139 --> 00:25:37.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then why am I here?</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:25:37.258 --> 00:25:40.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sisko to O'Brien.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Please report to my office.</i></c.bg_transparent>

362
00:25:40.257 --> 00:25:41.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On my way.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:25:42.377 --> 00:25:43.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, I don't know why you're here</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:25:44.616 --> 00:25:45.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I don't care.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:25:59.252 --> 00:26:00.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have a seat.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:26:07.729 --> 00:26:11.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand you had a confrontation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with Dr. Bashir yesterday.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:26:12.368 --> 00:26:13.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, that's a...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That was nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:26:14.167 --> 00:26:15.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not according to Dr. Bashir.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:26:16.207 --> 00:26:19.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We had a little argument.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Julian and I are always arguing.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:26:19.646 --> 00:26:22.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>According to Constable Odo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you also had an incident with Quark.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:26:23.205 --> 00:26:24.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did that little?</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:26:26.644 --> 00:26:29.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, sir, I may have let things get</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a little out of hand, but...</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:26:30.402 --> 00:26:31.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't happen again.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:26:31.682 --> 00:26:32.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm...</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:26:33.242 --> 00:26:36.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Bashir also tells me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you've stopped seeing your counselor.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:26:37.812 --> 00:26:38.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, I've been very busy lately--</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:26:38.480 --> 00:26:40.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The agreement was that you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were going to see a counselor</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:26:40.839 --> 00:26:41.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a regular basis.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:26:43.318 --> 00:26:44.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're right.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:26:44.598 --> 00:26:46.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll make an appointment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to go see him tomorrow.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:26:46.757 --> 00:26:47.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll see him today.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:26:49.357 --> 00:26:50.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:26:51.396 --> 00:26:52.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have a lot of work to do today, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:26:53.116 --> 00:26:54.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The work can wait.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:26:56.235 --> 00:26:58.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As of now, you're relieved of duty.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:26:58.754 --> 00:27:00.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to report to Counselor Telnorri</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:27:00.953 --> 00:27:03.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and begin attending</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>daily counseling sessions</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:27:03.472 --> 00:27:05.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for as long as he thinks it's advisable.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:27:06.432 --> 00:27:08.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, you're blowing this all</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out of proportion.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:27:08.910 --> 00:27:10.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know that's not true.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:27:10.750 --> 00:27:12.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to you on Argratha</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:27:12.550 --> 00:27:14.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>affected you a lot more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than you're willing to admit</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:27:14.989 --> 00:27:16.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it's not going to get better overnight</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:27:16.788 --> 00:27:18.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>no matter how much you want it to.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:27:19.308 --> 00:27:20.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You need help.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:27:21.507 --> 00:27:22.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:27:23.827 --> 00:27:28.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking you as a personal favor to me.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Give me one more chance.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:27:31.304 --> 00:27:32.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish I could.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:27:34.743 --> 00:27:35.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But right now</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:27:35.863 --> 00:27:38.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>in the judgment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of this station's Chief Medical Officer</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:27:39.142 --> 00:27:42.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you're unfit for duty</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>which means you're on medical leave</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:27:43.607 --> 00:27:44.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>effective immediately</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:27:44.340 --> 00:27:46.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and if you don't begin attending</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>counseling sessions</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:27:46.939 --> 00:27:47.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>on a regular basis</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:27:48.596 --> 00:27:50.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and cooperating in every</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>other way with your physician</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:27:50.979 --> 00:27:52.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will have no choice</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:27:52.338 --> 00:27:54.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but to have you confined</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:27:54.577 --> 00:27:55.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that clear?</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:27:57.566 --> 00:27:58.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, sir.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:28:01.295 --> 00:28:02.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dismissed.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:28:11.932 --> 00:28:14.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, I was just about to head down</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Replimat...</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:28:14.852 --> 00:28:16.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not now, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:28:19.370 --> 00:28:20.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Promenade.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:28:28.207 --> 00:28:29.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What the hell did you say to him?</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:28:30.473 --> 00:28:31.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I take it you talked to Captain Sisko.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:28:31.846 --> 00:28:32.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I talked to him, all right.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:28:33.326 --> 00:28:35.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He relieved me of duty.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's for the best, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:28:36.453 --> 00:28:37.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you know what's best for me?</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:28:38.444 --> 00:28:40.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have no idea what I've been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>going through!</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:28:40.363 --> 00:28:43.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're right. You were alone in that cell.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I wasn't there with you.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:28:43.443 --> 00:28:45.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't see what they did to you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I do know you suffered</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:28:46.195 --> 00:28:48.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and that you're still suffering now,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm trying to help.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:28:48.641 --> 00:28:50.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never asked for your help.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:28:50.440 --> 00:28:53.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You didn't need to ask.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm your doctor and your friend.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:28:54.239 --> 00:28:55.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>EE'CHAR: You should listen to him, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:28:56.119 --> 00:28:58.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He cares about you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just like I did.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:28:58.478 --> 00:29:00.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't make the same mistake with him</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you did with me.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:29:02.797 --> 00:29:04.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you get it?</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:29:04.916 --> 00:29:07.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not my friend! Not anymore!</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:29:08.435 --> 00:29:10.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The O'Brien that was your friend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>died in that cell!</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:29:11.314 --> 00:29:12.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not dead.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:29:13.354 --> 00:29:15.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He just needs a little help</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that's all.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:29:16.329 --> 00:29:17.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stay away from me.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:29:18.272 --> 00:29:20.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want your help,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want your friendship</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:29:21.111 --> 00:29:22.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just want to be left alone!</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:29:26.190 --> 00:29:28.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where are you going?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I told you to go away!</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:29:28.349 --> 00:29:31.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, please, don't do this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Go back there and talk to him.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:29:31.668 --> 00:29:32.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He wants to help you.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:29:32.708 --> 00:29:34.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Like you did?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's right.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:29:34.628 --> 00:29:37.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We're both your friends.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeah, and look what happened to you.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:29:38.426 --> 00:29:39.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Habitat Ring.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:29:46.623 --> 00:29:49.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know, sooner or later</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll have to tell someone about me.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:29:49.663 --> 00:29:50.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like hell I will.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:29:52.226 --> 00:29:54.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't run from me forever.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:29:55.661 --> 00:29:56.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're dead</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:29:56.860 --> 00:29:58.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>so why don't you go away</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and leave me alone?</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:29:59.420 --> 00:30:01.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want me to leave?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll leave!</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:30:01.499 --> 00:30:02.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Send me away!</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:30:03.991 --> 00:30:04.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see?</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:30:04.338 --> 00:30:07.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I keep coming back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's because some part of you</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:30:07.417 --> 00:30:08.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>keeps bringing me here!</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:30:23.853 --> 00:30:26.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles, Julian's been trying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to contact you for an hour.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:30:26.452 --> 00:30:29.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where have you been?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Walking. Thinking.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:30:29.211 --> 00:30:31.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know. I heard. I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:30:32.506 --> 00:30:35.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I know how much your work means to you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Try telling that to Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:30:36.449 --> 00:30:38.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy, come see what I drew.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:30:39.328 --> 00:30:42.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Not now, honey, okay?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm sure it's only temporary.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:30:42.287 --> 00:30:43.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be back at work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>before you know it.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:30:44.727 --> 00:30:45.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy, you have to come see.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:30:45.805 --> 00:30:47.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, can we talk about this later?</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:30:47.566 --> 00:30:49.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Daddy, come on!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Not now.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:30:49.405 --> 00:30:52.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Please, Daddy, please!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I said not now, right?</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:30:52.204 --> 00:30:54.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I said not!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Miles! What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:30:55.883 --> 00:30:58.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, shh, shh.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:31:00.801 --> 00:31:01.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't mean to...</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:31:01.881 --> 00:31:03.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shh.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:31:04.800 --> 00:31:06.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:32:27.535 --> 00:32:28.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief?</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:32:31.894 --> 00:32:33.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get out of here, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:32:35.213 --> 00:32:36.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want to do this, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:32:38.332 --> 00:32:39.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The hell I don't.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:32:42.131 --> 00:32:44.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, I don't claim to know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you're going through</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:32:44.570 --> 00:32:46.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but whatever it is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's not worth dying for.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:32:49.849 --> 00:32:51.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't understand at all.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:32:53.607 --> 00:32:54.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not doing this for me.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:32:56.870 --> 00:33:00.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm doing it to protect Keiko and Molly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and everyone else in this station.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:33:01.365 --> 00:33:03.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Protect us from what?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-From me.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:33:06.564 --> 00:33:08.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not the man I used to be.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:33:10.339 --> 00:33:11.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm dangerous.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:33:15.721 --> 00:33:17.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I nearly hit Molly today.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:33:18.121 --> 00:33:19.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All she wanted was a little attention</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:33:20.840 --> 00:33:22.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I nearly hit her.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:33:23.478 --> 00:33:24.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you didn't.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:33:26.718 --> 00:33:28.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're a good man, Miles Edward O'Brien</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:33:30.356 --> 00:33:32.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and whatever it is you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've done wrong</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:33:32.356 --> 00:33:33.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you don't deserve to die.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:33:34.116 --> 00:33:35.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sound like Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:33:36.315 --> 00:33:37.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who's Ee'Char?</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:33:40.274 --> 00:33:42.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's... not real.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:33:46.872 --> 00:33:48.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's just a memory, that's all.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:33:49.231 --> 00:33:50.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A memory from Argratha?</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:33:52.706 --> 00:33:54.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Who was he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Another prisoner? A guard?</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:33:56.293 --> 00:33:57.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was my cell mate.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:33:58.588 --> 00:34:00.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You told me you were alone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in that cell.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:34:01.282 --> 00:34:02.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Twenty years with no one to talk to.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:34:10.104 --> 00:34:15.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was at the end, a week... two maybe.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:34:18.502 --> 00:34:19.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But the rest of the time...</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:34:21.701 --> 00:34:22.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:34:25.140 --> 00:34:26.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What happened to him?</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:34:30.858 --> 00:34:32.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( distant yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:34:32.618 --> 00:34:33.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah...</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:34:33.977 --> 00:34:35.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why'd you do that?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:34:41.336 --> 00:34:42.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't helping.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:34:43.694 --> 00:34:45.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You need to concentrate more.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:34:45.694 --> 00:34:49.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't matter how much I concentrate.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm still starving.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:34:50.773 --> 00:34:52.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:34:53.118 --> 00:34:54.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So am I.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:34:55.411 --> 00:34:57.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sure there's nothing left?</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:34:57.331 --> 00:35:00.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not unless you have a hiding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>place I don't know about.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:35:00.409 --> 00:35:03.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We ate the last of the food</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I put away a week ago.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:35:06.874 --> 00:35:07.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should have stockpiled more.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:35:08.727 --> 00:35:10.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should have prepared for this.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:35:10.927 --> 00:35:13.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They've never let us go this long</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without food before.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:35:14.125 --> 00:35:19.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe they've forgotten about us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or just decided to finally let us die.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:35:22.762 --> 00:35:23.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then we die.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:35:24.722 --> 00:35:27.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARGRATHI: ( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>over PA </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>) </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>All offenders</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>prepare for dormancy period.</i></c.bg_transparent>

517
00:35:27.682 --> 00:35:30.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Any offender still active</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>during the dormancy period</i></c.bg_transparent>

518
00:35:30.241 --> 00:35:31.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>will be disciplined.</i></c.bg_transparent>

519
00:35:31.361 --> 00:35:34.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Illumination will be suspended</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>in 20 seconds.</i></c.bg_transparent>

520
00:35:35.679 --> 00:35:36.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:35:37.359 --> 00:35:38.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to sleep.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:35:38.878 --> 00:35:43.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How can you sleep at a time like this?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Maybe I'll dream about food.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:35:45.316 --> 00:35:46.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're crazy.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:35:46.676 --> 00:35:47.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No...</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:35:48.955 --> 00:35:49.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just hungry.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:35:51.749 --> 00:35:52.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARGRATHI: ( </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>over PA </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>)</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i></i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Dormancy period initiated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

527
00:36:43.859 --> 00:36:44.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( yelling )</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:36:48.577 --> 00:36:50.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You pretended to be my friend</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:36:50.857 --> 00:36:53.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and all the time you were holding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>out on me.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:36:53.255 --> 00:36:54.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now who's acting crazy?</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:37:01.294 --> 00:37:04.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After everything I've done for you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you ungrateful...</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:37:19.808 --> 00:37:20.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( bones crunching )</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:37:32.964 --> 00:37:34.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling )</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:37:35.324 --> 00:37:36.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You...</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:37:37.603 --> 00:37:40.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were saving it for both of us.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:37:47.200 --> 00:37:48.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:37:50.838 --> 00:37:52.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char, wake up.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:38:04.115 --> 00:38:05.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ee'Char... Ee'Char...</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:38:08.713 --> 00:38:09.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You killed him?</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:38:14.191 --> 00:38:15.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The worst part of it was...</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:38:16.511 --> 00:38:20.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The next day, the guards</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>began feeding me again.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:38:22.709 --> 00:38:23.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I killed him for nothing,</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:38:25.229 --> 00:38:27.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for a scrap of bread</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he was going to share with me.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:38:28.387 --> 00:38:30.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it was a mistake. You didn't mean it.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:38:33.185 --> 00:38:34.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I meant it.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:38:35.545 --> 00:38:37.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted him to die.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:38:39.464 --> 00:38:41.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I keep telling myself...</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:38:42.503 --> 00:38:43.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't matter.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:38:43.863 --> 00:38:45.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It wasn't real.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:38:45.782 --> 00:38:46.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But that's a lie.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:38:47.861 --> 00:38:49.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it had been real, if it had been you</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:38:49.741 --> 00:38:50.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>instead of him</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:38:51.300 --> 00:38:53.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>it wouldn't have made any difference.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:38:54.204 --> 00:38:57.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was my best friend and I murdered him.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:39:00.298 --> 00:39:03.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When we were growing up,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they used to tell us...</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:39:04.567 --> 00:39:05.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Humanity had evolved</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:39:07.959 --> 00:39:11.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that mankind had outgrown hate and rage.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:39:14.414 --> 00:39:15.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But when it came down to it</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:39:16.893 --> 00:39:21.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>when I had the chance to show</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that no matter what anyone did to me</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:39:21.531 --> 00:39:24.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was still an evolved human being...</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:39:26.370 --> 00:39:27.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I failed.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:39:30.569 --> 00:39:33.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I repaid kindness with blood.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:39:37.366 --> 00:39:39.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was no better than an animal.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:39:39.726 --> 00:39:40.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. No, no, no.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:39:41.205 --> 00:39:42.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>An animal would've killed Ee'Char</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:39:42.725 --> 00:39:45.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and never had a second thought,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>never shed a tear</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:39:45.844 --> 00:39:47.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but not you. You hate yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:39:48.763 --> 00:39:51.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You hate yourself so much you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you deserve to die.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:39:52.402 --> 00:39:55.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Argrathi did everything they could</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to strip you of your humanity</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:39:56.560 --> 00:39:59.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and in the end, for one brief moment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they succeeded.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:40:00.320 --> 00:40:03.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you can't let that brief moment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>define your entire life.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:40:04.118 --> 00:40:08.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you do, if you pull that trigger</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then the Argrathi will have won.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:40:09.597 --> 00:40:15.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They will have destroyed a good man.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You cannot let that happen, my friend.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:40:29.671 --> 00:40:30.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:40:32.950 --> 00:40:34.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be well, Miles.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:40:58.942 --> 00:41:01.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thirty milligrams twice a day.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Take it religiously for a month.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:41:01.222 --> 00:41:03.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And if all goes well</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'll experiment with a lower dosage.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:41:03.261 --> 00:41:04.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sure this'll work?</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:41:04.261 --> 00:41:07.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a treatment, not a cure.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It'll prevent hallucinations</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:41:07.459 --> 00:41:09.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>take the edge off the depression</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but that's all it'll do.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:41:09.499 --> 00:41:11.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't take away the memories</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or the feelings.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:41:11.618 --> 00:41:12.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You mean the guilt.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:41:13.218 --> 00:41:14.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, that'll take time.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:41:16.457 --> 00:41:18.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now's the part where you tell me</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:41:18.377 --> 00:41:20.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to start seeing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Counselor Telnorri again.</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:41:21.559 --> 00:41:22.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unless you want to talk to me.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:41:23.614 --> 00:41:24.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Telnorri'll be fine.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:41:30.373 --> 00:41:32.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks, Julian... For everything.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:41:33.292 --> 00:41:34.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are friends for?</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:41:43.849 --> 00:41:46.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Daddy's home! Daddy's home!</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:41:53.206 --> 00:41:55.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right. Daddy's home.</c.bg_transparent>

